        "id": "sx_lot9_closed_hat_noise_cut_v0_25_13",
        "name": "Closed Hat Noise Cut",
        "category": "Percussive / Drums",
        "categoryCanonical": "Percussive / Drums",
        "description": "Hi-hat chiuso sintetico, costruito su noise filtrato, high-pass e decay molto breve.",
